title: NASA’s Hubble Sees Asteroids Colliding at Nearby Star for First Time
summary: Like a game of cosmic bumper cars, scientists think the early days of our solar system were a time of violent turmoil, with planetesimals, asteroids, and comets smashing together and pelting the Earth, Moon, and the other inner planets with debris.
